          </p>

          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong class="text-white">Assignment:</strong> You may not assign or transfer these Terms or your rights hereunder without our prior written consent. We may assign these Terms without restriction.
          </p>

          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong class="text-white">Force majeure:</strong> We are not liable for any delay or failure in performance resulting from causes beyond our reasonable control, including but not limited to natural disasters, acts of government, internet outages, or third-party service failures.
          </p>

